    definition: "An AI copilot is an artificial intelligence assistant that works alongside a human, providing suggestions, drafting content, analyzing data, or completing subtasks while the human maintains decision-making authority. Unlike AI agents that operate autonomously, copilots augment human capability without taking independent action.",
